short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Allows users to cycle through google search results by pressing the tab key.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This small extension brings familiar tab functionality back to the google search results page. Press tab once to go to the top result, or multiple times to cycle through the search results. Press enter on any result to view that result.
